com.elvenrings.qdemo.view.console

Class FillBlankConsoleRenderer

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.elvenrings.qdemo.view.AbstractRenderer
      • com.elvenrings.qdemo.view.console.DefaultConsoleRenderer
        • com.elvenrings.qdemo.view.console.FillBlankConsoleRenderer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ConsoleRenderer

    public class FillBlankConsoleRenderer
extends DefaultConsoleRenderer
    A ConsoleRenderer implementation that provides the following functionality:
    1. Renders the input prompt.
    2. Retrieves the console input and fires a FillBlankConsoleEvent to all registered listeners.
    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    Iliasu Salifu, iliasu@elvenrings.com
